# This file tells the instruction for using the code

1. Install Trilinos 

	(1) Download the Trilinos repos from the github website
	(2) Create a another seperate dir for build and Installation
	(3) Use the ubuntu-gcc-482-openmpi-cmake as the configure file
	(4) Install some supplimentary softwares according to configure log
		such as apt-get:
			gfortran, libblas-dev, liblapack-dev, python-numpy, python-scipy, python-matplotlib, swig3.0(compile and make install)
	(5) make -jN install (N is number of processors)
